## IMPORTANT NOTICE

This project includes code ported from PlayerStatueBuilder, which is licensed under
the GNU General Public License v3.0.

According to GPL v3.0 Section 2(b), because this work contains code from a GPL-3.0
licensed work, the entire work must be licensed under GPL-3.0.

### Ported Code from PlayerStatueBuilder

The following components are based on or inspired by PlayerStatueBuilder:
- Color difference algorithms (ColorMatcher.kt - ported from ColorDiffs.java)
- Image processing filters (ImageFilters.kt - ported from ImageUtil.java)
- Coordinate transformation logic (SchematicGenerator.kt, LitematicaGenerator.kt - based on FaceBuilder.java)
- Legacy conversion logic (SkinProcessor.kt - based on LegacyConverter.java)
- Coordinate mapping (following PlayerStatueBuilder's exact mapping)

